CVII. Any Sums may be Subſcribed (not leſs than 100 
                        l.
                     ) to be anſwered by Ten equal Payments, the Firſt Payment to be made at the time of Subſcribing, and each ſubſequent Payment ſhall be made at the end of every Two Months (or 60 Days) till the whole be paid; Nevertheleſs the laſt Payment ſhall be liable to make good any Deſiciency which may happen (before the time of making the laſt Payment) in the Produce of the ſaid Duties, although the Kings intended ſupply be thereby leſſened.
